<title type="html"><![CDATA[12/19(Thu.) Youtuber/New year resolutions (Host:Michael)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=344&amp;p=360#p360"><![CDATA[
Session I<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://grow.grin.co/should-i-become-a-youtuber/">https://grow.grin.co/should-i-become-a-youtuber/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. What are the pros and cons of being a YouTuber?<br />2. Which YouTuber do you like most? Why?<br />3. Do you think being a YouTuber worth it?<br />4. Do YouTubers have good or bad influence on our society?<br />5. How do think some people use YouTube channel to lead viewers' thought?<br /><br />Session II<br /> <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://daringtolivefully.com/new-year-resolution-ideas">https://daringtolivefully.com/new-year-resolution-ideas</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br /><br />1. Do you fulfill your 2019 resolutions?   If yes, congratulations, if not, what reasons hinder you from accomplishing? <br />2. What are your 2020 new year's resolutions?   Any practical plans to execute them?<br />3. What are some New Year's resolutions that people will break quickly?<br />4. Is it useful by using dream board or vision board to fulfill our resolutions?<br />5. Do you have any tips to help people's new year's resolutions succeed? <br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 p.m. --7:20 p.m. Free talk<br />7:20 p.m. --7:50 p.m. First topic discussion<br />7:50 p.m. --8:15 p.m. Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited)<br />8:15p.m.-- 8:45 p.m. Second topic discussion<br />8:45 p.m.-- 9:00 p.m. Presentation (Participants that haven't presented yet are invited)<br />speaker time: 2 minutes for each speaker<br />host time: 3 minutes<br /><br />The meeting place of Thursday:<br />丹堤咖啡寶慶店：台北市延平南路107號2F (上樓右邊第三區塊)<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運–西門站 (4號出口步行約2分鐘，康是美隔壁)<br />丹堤低消: NT$80元<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500，帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=13721">morris</a> — Fri Dec 13, 2019 9:58 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
